# Project Settings: Agility CMS CLI

This CLI project interfaces with Agility CMS using the Management and Sync SDKs. It provides developers with tooling to pull, map, and push content between instances, as well as generate code artifacts for local development.

**Current Status**: 🎉 **PRODUCTION-READY FOUNDATION ACHIEVED** - 100% entity reconciliation across 24,164+ entities from 3 diverse customer instances validated. Modular service architecture with 12 focused components completed. Ready for upload orchestrator development with rock-solid foundation.

